<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> Yu, Neng; et al. <a href="http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/short/346/20/1545?query=TOC" class="external text" title="http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/short/346/20/1545?query=TOC" rel="nofollow">"Disputed Maternity Leading to Identification of Tetragametic Chimerism"</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_New_England_Journal_of_Medicine" title="The New England Journal of Medicine" class="mw-redirect">The New England Journal of Medicine</a></i>, 346:1545-1552, 16 May 2002.</li>
<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://users.rcn.com/jkimball.ma.ultranet/BiologyPages/M/Mosaics.html#TetragameticHuman" class="external text" title="http://users.rcn.com/jkimball.ma.ultranet/BiologyPages/M/Mosaics.html#TetragameticHuman" rel="nofollow">"Genetic Mosaics: A Tetragametic Human"</a></li>
</ol>
